verbose_text: On day 24 of differentiation, in which the OLCs were developed, the mRNA levels of SCP3, GDF9, ZP1, ZP2 and ZP3 increased by approxiamtely 6-fold (P = 0.039), 3.5-fold (P = 0.007), 4-fold (P = 0.014), 1.33-fold (P = 0.036), and 8-fold (P = 0.008), respectively, when compared to the levels obtained on day 0 (XREF_FIG).
evidence: levels of SCP3, GDF9, ZP1, ZP2
